Digitally remastered and expanded three disc (two CD + DVD) edition of the Progressive Metal band's 1994 album. Disc One features the remastered edition of the original album. Disc Two features twelve live and demo tracks. Disc Three (DVD) contains live footage of the band performing the album and other FW favorites during their 1994-95 tour.
